               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Malkǝʾa ʿAbiyä ʾƎgziʾ “Image of ʿAbiyä ʾƎgziʾ” (fols. 1v-8v) (ChRep
                     191, no. 19)
 II) Malkǝʾa ʾIyasus “Image of Jesus” (fols. 8v-29v) (ChRep
                     199, no. 123)
 III) Malkǝʾa Takla Hāymānot “Image of Takla Haymanot” (fols.
                     31r-52v) (ChRep 339, no. 211)
 IV) Sǝbḥāta fǝqur za-Mikāʾel “Praise of the
                     Beloved for Mikāʾel” (section of Horologium) (fols. 53r-59v), (cp. EMML no.
                     5907).</summary>
